fol_ps: exists x. (Person(x) & WearingStrawHat(x) & SmokingCigarette(x))
nl_h: A dog is near the red ball in the air
fol_h: exists x.exists y. (Dog(x) & RedBall(y) & Near(x, y))
label: n

nl_ps: A woman is riding a horse
fol_ps: exists x. exists y. (Woman(x) & Horse(y) & Riding(x, y))
nl_h: A boy in blue are sliding down a green slide
fol_h: all x.all y.all z. (Boy(x) & Blue(x) & GreenSlide(y) & Slide(z) -> SlidingDown(x, y, z))
label: n

nl_ps: A man is drawing some figures
fol_ps: exists x. (Man(x) & DrawingFigures(x))

label: n

nl_ps: The people are walking on the road beside a beautiful waterfall

fol_h: exists x. (Dog(x) & White(x) & Brown(x) & WalkingThroughWater(x))

nl_ps: The young girl is blowing a bubble that is huge

nl_ps: A boy is happily playing the piano

nl_ps: The girl, who is little, is combing her hair into a pony tail.

nl_h: Two people wearing helmets are driving over the yellow and white flowers

nl_ps: A man is in a parking lot and is playing tennis against a large wall
